    "width": 300,
    "z": 10075,
    "movable": false,
    "text": "This scoreboard uses the 'rounds' property to name the rounds. The default is sequential whole numbers starting at 1, but you can specifiy anything, including text. It also sets the 'showAllRounds' property to true. Since there is only data for 6 rounds in each seat, the 7th round ('Not Used Yet') is displayed, but shows blank. If left false, the widget would only show 6 rows of data. ",
